Title: Hitchhiking from Portugal to France
DateModified: '2019-03-08'
DatePublished: '2019-03-08'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/hitchhiking-from-portugal-to-france
SetInCountry: France
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Cathy Egge
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "I'm a 61 year old disabled retiree from Minnesota. I'm at the time in life\
  \ when I need to decide where my life will end.  I found a piece of property that\
  \ I'd really love to look at. It's affordable and I know it needs work, but what\
  \ else do I have to do?  It is here:  https://www.french-property.com/sale-property/1536-3336AG.\
  \ Please have a look. I used to hitchhike as a kid and I'm pretty fearless, so...I'm\
  \ ready to roll! If you get me to Portugal, I'll keep as accurate a journal as I'm\
  \ able. I plan to strike the nay-sayers with wonderment! How did I ever do it? I'm\
  \ sorry, Darling! It's in the stars. I could do 708 miles in my sleep!\n\n Serendipitally\
  \ Yours,\n\n Cathy\n\n\nPS  If you think this is ridiculous, you're NO FUN."
